  export const frd = 
  "# **Education Management Platform**\n\n---\n\n## **1. System Overview**\n\nA comprehensive education management platform supporting three user roles: Student, Tutor, and Admin, with AI-powered features for learning, assessment, and administration.\n\n---\n\n## **2. User Roles & Authentication**\n\n### **2.1 User Roles**\n\n- **Student:** Learners who access educational content, tutors, and AI-powered learning tools  \n- **Tutor:** Educators who manage students, create assessments, and provide feedback  \n- **Admin:** System administrators with full access to manage the platform  \n\n### **2.2 Authentication Features**\n\n- Email/password signup and login  \n- Role-based access control (RBAC)  \n- Role-specific onboarding flows  \n- Profile management with user preferences  \n\n---\n\n## **3. Core Modules**\n\n### **3.1 Mail Module**  \n**Available to:** All roles  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- Full-screen compose interface  \n- Send messages to multiple recipients  \n- File attachments support  \n- Message categories: general, assignment, feedback, announcement, meeting  \n- Reply to messages  \n- Mark as read/unread  \n- Archive messages  \n- Message detail view with conversation threading  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Users can only view messages they sent or received  \n- Senders can create attachments  \n- Recipients can view attachments  \n\n---\n\n### **3.2 Calendar Module**  \n**Available to:** All roles  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- Create and manage events  \n- Event types: lesson, assessment, meeting, deadline, holiday, other  \n- Recurring events support  \n- Event attendees management  \n- Link events to curriculum (subject, grade, curriculum)  \n- Event status tracking: scheduled, completed, cancelled, postponed  \n- Reminder notifications  \n- Location management: online/physical  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Users can manage events they created  \n- Users can view events they're invited to  \n- Admins can manage all events  \n\n---\n\n### **3.3 Attendance Module**  \n**Available to:** Tutors, Admins  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- Manual attendance marking  \n- AI-powered OCR attendance processing from images  \n- Attendance status: present, absent, late, excused  \n- Bulk attendance upload  \n- Attendance history tracking  \n- AI confidence scoring for OCR-processed records  \n- Notes for attendance entries  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Students can view their own attendance  \n- Tutors can manage attendance for assigned students  \n- Admins can manage all attendance records  \n\n---\n\n### **3.4 Files Module**  \n**Available to:** All roles  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- File upload and management  \n- File categories: lecture_notes, assignments, readings, resources, other  \n- File sharing with specific users  \n- Public/private file visibility  \n- Download tracking  \n- File organization by curriculum, grade, and subject  \n- File type and size tracking  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Uploaders can manage their own files  \n- Users can view files shared with them  \n- Everyone can view public files  \n- Admins have full access  \n\n---\n\n### **3.5 Feedback Module**  \n**Available to:** Students, Tutors  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- Send feedback messages between tutors and students  \n- Feedback types: performance, assignment, behavior, general, progress  \n- Link feedback to specific subjects  \n- Reply to feedback (threaded conversations)  \n- File attachments support  \n- Read/unread status tracking  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Users can send and view feedback they're involved in  \n- Recipients can update read status  \n\n---\n\n### **3.6 Reports Module**  \n**Available to:** Students (view), Tutors (create/view)  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- AI-generated progress reports  \n- Manual report generation by tutors  \n- Report metrics:\n  - Overall grade  \n  - Attendance percentage  \n  - Assignments completed/total  \n  - Strengths analysis  \n  - Areas for improvement  \n  - AI-powered insights  \n  - Tutor comments  \n- Date range selection for reports  \n- Report period tracking  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Students can view their own reports  \n- Tutors can create and view reports for assigned students  \n- Admins have full access  \n\n---\n\n### **3.7 Assessments Dashboard**  \n**Available to:** Students, Tutors  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- Create and manage assessments  \n- Question bank management  \n- Pre-test and post-test support  \n- Assessment configuration: time limits, max attempts, passing score, question randomization  \n- Immediate results display  \n- Assessment attempts tracking  \n- AI-powered grading  \n- Manual grading interface  \n- Rubric-based evaluation  \n- Performance analytics  \n\n**Question Types Supported:**\n\n- Multiple choice  \n- Short answer  \n- Essay  \n- True/false  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Students can view active assessments and take them  \n- Tutors can create, manage, and grade assessments  \n- Students can view their own attempts and results  \n\n---\n\n### **3.8 AI Tutor Module**  \n**Available to:** Students  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- Subject Selection: Choose learning topics (English, Math, Science, etc.)  \n- Voice Conversation: Real-time AI conversation practice  \n- Speaking Exercises: Pronunciation and fluency practice  \n- Interactive Exercises: Practice questions with AI feedback  \n- Learning Paths: Personalized learning journeys\n  - Structured lessons  \n  - Progress tracking  \n  - Current lesson management  \n  - Lesson completion tracking  \n- Progress Dashboard: Visualize learning metrics\n  - Total sessions  \n  - Speaking time  \n  - Points earned  \n  - Current streak  \n  - Level progression  \n  - Badges earned  \n  - Session history  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Users can only access their own learning data  \n- All learning progress is user-specific  \n\n---\n\n### **3.9 Tutor Marketplace**  \n**Available to:** Students (browse/book), Tutors (manage profile/bookings)  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- Tutor Discovery: search/filter tutors, view ratings, subject expertise, availability, hourly rate, service location  \n- Booking System: schedule lessons, select duration and subject, choose location, add special notes, payment integration (Stripe), booking status tracking  \n- Booking Management: view upcoming/past bookings, confirm/cancel bookings, add meeting links, track payment status  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Public tutor profile viewing  \n- Students can create bookings  \n- Tutors and students can manage their bookings  \n\n---\n\n### **3.10 Quiz Generator**  \n**Available to:** Tutors  \n\n**Features:**\n\n- AI-powered quiz generation  \n- Configuration options: subject, grade, curriculum, topic, difficulty, number of questions, question type  \n- Quiz storage and management  \n- Generated quiz metadata tracking  \n\n**Access Control:**\n\n- Tutors can create and view quizzes  \n- Admins can manage all quizzes  \n\n---\n\n## **4. Dashboard Features**\n\n### **4.1 Student Dashboard**\n\n- Overview of assigned tutors  \n- Access to all student modules  \n- Quick access to AI tutor features  \n- View bookings and schedule  \n- Assessment notifications  \n\n### **4.2 Tutor Dashboard**\n\n- Student management  \n- Access to tutor-specific modules  \n- Booking management  \n- Assessment creation and grading  \n- Progress report generation  \n\n### **4.3 Landing Page**\n\n- Public-facing homepage  \n- Login/signup options  \n- Platform overview for unauthenticated users  \n\n---\n\n## **5. Onboarding System**\n\n### **5.1 Student Onboarding**\n\n- Curriculum selection  \n- Grade level selection  \n- Subject preferences  \n- Learning goals setup  \n\n### **5.2 Tutor Onboarding**\n\n- Profile creation  \n- Curriculum expertise setup  \n- Subject and grade specialization  \n- Availability configuration  \n- Rate setting  \n- Service area definition  \n\n---\n\n## **6. Admin Features**\n\n### **6.1 Tutor-Student Assignment Management**\n\n- Manual tutor-student assignments  \n- Auto-matching system based on subject expertise, curriculum alignment, grade level, availability, rating, experience  \n- Assignment status management  \n- Assignment history tracking  \n\n### **6.2 Admin Actions Logging**\n\n- Track all admin actions  \n- Record action types, targets, and reasons  \n- Maintain audit trail for compliance  \n\n---\n\n## **7. AI-Powered Features**\n\n### **7.1 AI Grading**\n\n- Automated assessment grading  \n- Rubric-based evaluation  \n- Confidence scoring  \n- Human review flagging  \n- Feedback generation  \n\n### **7.2 AI Progress Reports**\n\n- Automated analysis of student performance  \n- Data synthesis from attendance records, assessment scores, assignment completion  \n- AI-generated insights: strengths, areas for improvement, personalized recommendations  \n\n### **7.3 AI Quiz Generation**\n\n- Curriculum-aligned question generation  \n- Multiple difficulty levels  \n- Various question formats  \n\n### **7.4 AI OCR Processing**\n\n- Attendance image processing  \n- Student name recognition  \n- Status extraction  \n\n---\n\n## **8. Data Management**\n\n### **8.1 Curriculum System**\n\n- Multiple curricula support  \n- Grade levels management  \n- Subject organization  \n- Curriculum-subject relationships  \n\n### **8.2 Notification System**\n\n- In-app notifications  \n- Event-based triggers  \n- Read/unread status  \n- Notification categories  \n\n### **8.3 Review System**\n\n- Tutor ratings and reviews  \n- Anonymous review option  \n- Tutor responses to reviews  \n- Review moderation  \n\n---\n\n## **9. Security Features**\n\n- Row-Level Security (RLS) on all tables  \n- Security definer functions to prevent recursion  \n- Role-based access control  \n- Secure file storage with access policies  \n- Payment security (Stripe integration)  \n- User data isolation  \n\n---\n\n## **10. Technical Architecture**\n\n### **10.1 Frontend**\n\n- React with TypeScript  \n- Tailwind CSS with design system tokens  \n- React Router for navigation  \n- React Query for data fetching  \n- Shadcn UI components  \n\n### **10.2 Backend**\n\n- Supabase (PostgreSQL database)  \n- Row-Level Security policies  \n- Edge Functions for AI grading, progress report generation, quiz generation, OCR processing, auto-matching  \n- Storage buckets for file management  \n\n### **10.3 Integrations**\n\n- Lovable AI API for AI features  \n- Stripe for payments  \n- Resend for email notifications  \n\n---\n\n**Document Version:** 1.0  \n**Last Updated:** 2025-10-24  \n**Status:** Active Development\n\n\n\n"
